### Spacewalk 2.6 setup

The 2.6 flow is the same, run with `spacewalk-setup --external-oracle`. Note the database may first reject an invalid credential before succeeding:

```console
# spacewalk-setup --external-oracle
...
Global Database Name or SID (requires tnsnames.ora)? swdb.oradb01.example.net
Database hostname [localhost]? oradb01.example.net
Username? swalk_user
Password?
*** Database connection error: ORA-01017: invalid username/password; logon denied (DBD ERROR: OCISessionBegin)
Username? swalk_user
Password?
** Database: Testing database connection.
** Database: Populating database.
...
Installation complete.
Visit https://spacewalk01.example.net to create the Spacewalk administrator account.
```

